\c 12
\s Mambo Shishaki anorwa naRehobhoamu
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika Rehobhoamu asimbisa ushe, uye azvisimbisa, wakasiya murairo waJehovha, naIsraeri wese pamwe naye.
\p
\v 2 Zvino zvakaitika mugore rechishanu ramambo Rehobhoamu, Shishaki mambo weEgipita wakakwira kurwisana neJerusarema, nokuti vakadarika kuna Jehovha,
\v 3 ane ngoro churu nemazana maviri, nevatasvi vemabhiza zvuru makumi matanhatu, nevanhu vaiva vasungaverengeki vaiva vauya naye kubva kuEgipita: VaRibhiya, vaSukimi, neVaKushi.
\v 4 Akakunda maguta enhare aJudha, ndokuuya kuJerusarema.
\p
\v 5 Zvino kwakuya Shemaya muporofita kuna Rehobhoamu nemisoro yaJudha yaiva yakaungana paJerusarema ne nekuda kwaShishaki, ndokuti kwavari: Ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha: Makandisiya, saka ndakakurasiraiwo muruoko rwaShishaki.
\v 6 Zvino machinda aIsraeri namambo vakazvininipisa, ndokuti: Jehovha wakarurama.
\v 7 Zvino Jehovha paakaona kuti vazvininipisa, shoko raJehovha rikasvika kuna Shemaya richiti: Vazvininipisa, handingavaparadzi, asi ndichavapa kakurwira; uye kutsamwa kwangu hakungadururwi pamusoro peJerusarema neruoko rwaShishaki.
\v 8 Asi vachava varanda vake kuti vazive shumiro yangu neshumiro yeushe hwedzinyika.
\v 9 Naizvozvo Shishaki mambo weEgipita wakakwira kurwisa Jerusarema, ndokutora zvinokosha zveimba yaJehovha nezvinokosha zveimba yamambo; wakazvitora zvese; akatorawo nhovo diki dzegoridhe dzakaitwa naSoromoni.
\v 10 Mambo Rehobhoamu ndokuita nhovo diki dzendarira pachinzvimbo chadzo, ndokupa pasi peruoko rwevakuru vevarindi, vaichengetedza mukova weimba yamambo.
\v 11 Zvino mambo paaipinda muimba yaJehovha, varindi vaiuya ndokudzisimudza ndokudzidzosera mukamuri revarindi.
\v 12 Zvino paakazvininipisa, kutsamwa kwaJehovha kwakadzoka kubva kwaari, kuti asaparadza chose; uye kwaJudha kwakava nezvinhu zvakanaka.
\p
\v 13 Zvino mambo Rehobhoamu wakazvisimbisa paJerusarema, ndokutonga; nokuti Rehobhomu waiva wemakore makumi mana nerimwe paakatanga kutonga, ndokutonga paJerusarema makore gumi nemanomwe, guta Jehovha raakasarudza kubva pamarudzi ese aIsraeri, kuisa zita rakepo; zita ramai vake raiva Naama muAmoni.
\v 14 Zvino wakaita chinhu chakaipa, nokuti waiva sina kugadzirira hana yake kutsvaka Jehovha.
\v 15 Zvino dzimwe nyaya dzaRehobhoamu, dzekutanga nedzekupedzisira, hadzina kunyorwa here mumashoko emuporofita Shemaya, neemuoni Idho, maererano nemadzinza? Zvino pakava ne nedzihondo dzaRehobhoamu naJerobhoamu nguva dzese.
\v 16 Rehobhoamu ndokurara nemadzibaba ake, ndokuvigwa muguta raDhavhidhi; Abhija mwanakomana wake ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake.
